<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>We see his creativity reflected in his writing, which is often full of his imaginative thinking, as well as imagery, magic, and his unique writer&rsquo;s voice. His love for reading fantasy and adventure shows in the way he wisely models great author&rsquo;s styles in his work. He uses writing tools independently and can capably craft a solidly written piece. He should continue to work on using revision to add details and tighten his focus by adding transitional sentences. Marlo takes editing seriously and should continue to carefully ;reader_notes=;notes=;status=0;submit=Save Section;

