<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Olivia&rsquo;s writing contains flashes of her creativity, but she often stops short of the really detailed pieces of which she is capable. We would like to see her challenge herself to build her writing stamina and craft pieces that reflect her verbal ability. When she applies herself, her writing is full of her unique writer&rsquo;s voice, and she can use wri;reader_notes=;notes=;status=1;submit=Save Section;

