<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>Jack is conscientious about his reading assignments, but does not appear to enthusiastically read for pleasure. &nbsp;He can usually demonstrate his comprehension of the main story elements, particularly character traits, but does still need to work on relating the major plot points with key supporting details.&nbsp; We would like to see him continue to work on his reading skills to increase his comprehension by rereading to be sure he understands and interacting more with the ;reader_notes=;notes=;status=1;submit=Save Section;

